  <brief_title>Comparison of Chitosan and Carboxymethylcellulose Silver Dressings on Burn Wounds in Pediatric and Adult Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Randomized, Comparison Study of a Chitosan (Opticell Ag+) Silver Dressing and a Sodium Carboxymethylcellulose (AquacelÂ® Ag+) Silver Dressing on Burn Wounds in Pediatrics and Adults Subjects</official_title>
